snippet.title: Harry Potter: Quidditch Champions - Official Cinematic Trailer - “Let the Match Begin!"
snippet.description:
Brooms? Check! Robes? Check! Pre-Order? Check!

You’ll find yourself on the pitch in just two short days when #QuidditchChampions releases on
September 3rd! #backtohogwarts 

Pre-order the Standard or Deluxe Edition now on Xbox, Steam, & Epic Games Store to earn the
Firebolt Supreme Broom Skin. For PlayStation Plus* members, the Standard edition of
#QuidditchChampions and the Firebolt Supreme Broom Skin will be available as a redeemable
pack from 3 – 30th September 2024.

Pre-Order Now: https://go.wbgames.com/HPQCPreOrder
*Monthly games accessible for duration of PS Plus subscription only. PS Plus is an ongoing
subscription with recurring fees until canceled. Age restrictions apply. Full terms: play.st/psplus-
usageterms

Always be the first to get #QuidditchChampions news at https://bit.ly/3MeWr6v
#QuidditchChampions #HarryPotter #WizardingWorld #wbgames
